title: BGE LootLoot (F) v1.1.1
description:
Helping out my buddies at BusGasExplosion Studios, an independent development company, spreading their first Android game. This is the full free version with very minimal ads. The following is the description taken from their website:

LootLoot is the first in a series of arcade games to be released by BusGasExplosion Studios. Based on the classic game of Snake, play as an adventurer exploring ancient temple ruins and collect valuable treasure! Collecting at least 40 pieces of treasure will open up exit stairs to move onto the next level. Each new level becomes larger and more dangerous, as spiked traps and snake pits appear. As the adventurer continues the journey into the depths, more obstacles will appear to make treasure hunting harder.

LootLoot is available in two editions: Paid and Free.
